Company Profile:Zalora is the leading internet startup which is rapidly expanding in Southeast Asia. We are currently in 7 countries (Malaysia, Singapore, Indonesia, Thailand, Philippines, Vietnam and Hongkong). ZALORA.sg (www.zalora.sg) is one of the fastest growing e-commerce fashion retailer in Singapore! The company is a combination of a cool start-up environment where everyone bounces ideas of each other and a huge multinational corporation that has more than 1000 employees. We are looking for passionate people to join us and change the e-commerce landscape in Southeast Asia.
Job Description:Buying Intern (Temp to Full-Time)
The
Buying Assistant will work closely with the buying team in a vibrant
environment that fuses the dynamic worlds of fashion, technology and the
Internet.  The Assistant will have the opportunity to take on more
responsibility based on their previous knowledge and ability to learn on the
job. Assist with daily data processing. Assist in purchase order entry and
create and maintain weekly reportsSupport the Buying team by preparing
weekly selling reports to determine which items are selling/not selling.Visit the Zalora Warehouse
as & when required to support the logistics & operations team to sort
& count the shipments received.
Please apply for this position by submitting your cv and resume (in pdf) to Mansi.tolia@zalora.sg. Kindly note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.
